{"tid":1157390,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國正式拘捕　加國前外交官及商人","createTime":"2019-05-16T08:50:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-18T04:21:41.000Z","uid":47714,"like":171,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":60,"replies":[{"pid":"d6404d65cde1e6cccd2d557d3432a7d123d64df2","tid":1157390,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T08:50:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=348207\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D348207&d=nKoZ4xrs0zkQ%2F022jTHdf%2FS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=e82cbdaf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D348207&h=94dd44aa\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=348207</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】外交部證實，中國當局已正式拘捕兩名加拿大公民前外交官康明凱和商人斯帕弗。<br />\n<br />\n加拿大《環球郵報》早前引述政府消息報道，中國當局已正式拘捕康明凱和斯帕弗，並把他們由監視居住地方，轉移到正式的拘留中心，但兩人未收到正式拘控。<br />\n<br />\n報道又指在監視居住期間，康明凱和斯帕弗每天被盤問最多八個小時，房間內廿四小時都要開燈，兩人不准外出，亦不獲准與律師或家人接觸，每個月只可以與外交人員見面三十分鐘。<br />\n<br />\n中國電訊設備供應商華為的副董事長孟晚舟，去年十二月初被加拿大當局拘捕不久，康明凱和斯帕弗則在中國被捕，中方指兩人涉嫌從事危害國家安全活動。<br />\n<br />\n加拿大外交部發聲明，批評中方任意拘捕二人，要求立刻放人。"},{"pid":"49893363128e43375bec6184117ef2afb1fd8f94","tid":1157390,"uid":47714,"like":229,"dislike":1,"score":228,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T08:51:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10157113227192357\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcheng.lap.9%2Fposts%2F10157113227192357&d=nKoZ4xrs0zkQ%2F022jTHdf%2FS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=1602a37c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10157113227192357</a><br />\n<br />\n北京：「香港！come one baby！爭你個逃犯條例咋！」<br />\n香港：「我好興奮呀！我好興奮呀！」"},{"pid":"818fd7f4ad628b27cb12246f0eed3e3015120ca6","tid":1157390,"uid":113626,"like":133,"dislike":1,"score":132,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T08:51:38.000Z","msg":"真係決定同白人開戰 <img src=\"